{"tid":1542882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 如果我係林鄭 ....","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T04:02:53.000Z","uid":183525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46be2cdc3ae212e9429cba4428959ca245d6df0d","tid":1542882,"uid":183525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"9月4日，林鄭 LAG 機出招，只係按議事規則提出撤回動議，明顯係陰毒招數。<br />\n不如齊齊集思廣益推演一下，林鄭下一次出咩招數。<br />\n<br />\n小弟拋磚 !<br />\n<br />\n分析777 9月4 日的消息的兩大效果:  <br />\n第一 要搶走『反送中』運動的行動名義，令運動改名換幟，引起市民對社會運動反感。同樣地引導中外媒體對事件的描述，效果影響係更大，致命打擊國際戰線。<br />\n第二，拉出第一批<strong>投降派</strong>，動搖運動團結性，反之，政府多一把可用聲音。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭下一步 [9 月] : <br />\n比社會對 9月4日消息醞釀三兩日，期間保持警察暴力鎮壓，再答應『落實真普選』，相比另三訴求，成本最低，效果最為遠期，而且往後操作/ 騎劫空間最大。由此拉多一批<strong>投降派</strong>，削弱運動。等到十月一日可以保持市面平靜交到功課。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家推演長遠D 都OK ，集思廣益。"},{"pid":"00b24b931a5dad2965efb13c18ad25a2f31385c9","tid":1542882,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jp